DISCLAIMER (fan reimplementation)

ProsperityGamesa is an unofficial, independent fan reimplementation of the
mechanics of the game "Prosperity" (v0.9.5). It is NOT affiliated with,
endorsed by, or connected to the authors of the original game.

No protected content from the original is copied verbatim:
  - Game numbers, balance values, formulas and mechanics are treated as facts
    (not subject to copyright) and were extracted/derived from the original.
  - All prose, names, story, dialogue and achievement texts are original or
    paraphrased (provenance: original / original-paraphrased). A repeatable
    audit (tools/audit-provenance.mjs) confirms 0 verbatim matches against the
    original source.
  - Original source material under doc/original_source/ is used only as a
    research reference and is NOT distributed (excluded from the PWA precache
    manifest).

See PROVENANCE.md for the full provenance evidence.
